Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.76,0:24:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.91,0:24:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰顿 兰顿 兰顿～


